{"type":null,"faqId":11649,"title":"G610-U00(G610+)   发送彩信","answer":"<p>\n\t<span>1.<span style=\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">进入消息菜单，选择<b>新信息</b>，撰写新信息；</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span>2.<span style=\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">输入收件人和编辑消息内容；</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span>3.<span style=\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">按菜单键，再选择<b>添加主题</b>（添加主题后自动转换为彩信）；</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span>4.<span style=\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">点击文本框左边</span> <span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=33035\" width=\"23\" height=\"22\" alt=\"\" /></span><span>&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">按钮添加附件，可以加入图片、音频或视频（添加多媒体文件自动转成彩信）；</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span>5.<span style=\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">编辑完成后，点击<b>发送</b>。</span> \n</p>","faqTypeId":136,"faqType":"信息与邮件","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"2471","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-SMS-Email","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1398656444000,"seriesProductName":"G610-U00","visitedTimes":62,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keyword